Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.04,0:22:41.59,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}任憑此身沉浮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.21,0:22:45.05,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}你握緊冰冷的十指
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.05,0:22:47.92,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}臉上是悲切的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.92,0:22:50.89,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我無言以對
